data.description:
Great investment opportunity  in growing Sandy Springs/ Perimeter area. Very neutral home will fit any home buyer.  Great roommate floor plan with large bedrooms with matching walk in closets, vanity area and full bath.  Roomy, spacious, very smart layout. Must see.
Has great rental potential as well as small family or retirement property near the City. 



Neighborhood Description
Located in the ever-expanding city of Sandy Springs; one the most upscale cities in Fulton County.  This home is located between two Mercedes Bendz dealers and the Mercedes Benz corporate office.  Central to great shopping , excellent schools, and HQ to multiple Fortune 500 companies.  
Easy access to 400 & 285.  Comfortable distance from the City;  12 miles from State Farm and Mercedes Benz Stadiums and 8 miles from the SunTrust Stadium.  , malls, shopping, parks every thing is so close.
data.whatILove: Coffee on the patio during Spring time; the landscape is vibrant and well maintained.  The tennis court and swimming pool are always well kept. Quiet neighborhood.
